Package ro.isdc.wro.http.handler.factory

Interface Summary
RequestHandlerFactory Responsible for creating a RequestHandler's collection.
 

Class Summary
ConfigurableRequestHandlerFactory A RequestHandler implementation which is easy to configure using a Properties object.
DefaultRequestHandlerFactory Default RequestHandlerFactory which adds all RequestHandler's provided as spi by RequestHandlerProvider found in classpath.
SimpleRequestHandlerFactory A RequestHandlerFactory which holds RequestHandler's in a list.
